rM</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">)</a><a href=\"./Init/Core.html#Exists\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">it</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterM.IsPlausibleStep\">IsPlausibleStep</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterStep\">IterStep</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterM\">IterM</a> <span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">step</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.LawfulDeterministicIterator\">LawfulDeterministicIterator</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.LawfulDeterministicIterator.mk","kind":"ctor","line":961,"name":"Std.LawfulDeterministicIterator.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3b0f2862196c6a8af9eb0025ee650252694013dd/src/Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.lean#L961-L961"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">class</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.LawfulDeterministicIterator\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">LawfulDeterministicIterator</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> w}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> w)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> w → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> w'</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.Iterator\">Iterator</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"This typeclass characterizes iterators that have deterministic return values. This typeclass does\n*not* guarantee that there are no monadic side effects such as exceptions.\n\nGeneral monadic iterators can be nondeterministic, so that `it.IsPlausibleStep step` will be true\nfor no or more than one choice of `step`. This typeclass ensures that there is exactly one such\nchoice.\n\nThis is an experimental instance and it should not be explicitly used downstream of the standard\nlibrary.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.LawfulDeterministicIterator","kind":"class","line":950,"name":"Std.LawfulDeterministicIterator","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3b0f2862196c6a8af9eb0025ee650252694013dd/src/Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.lean#L950-L966"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.Iterators.instProductiveOfFinte\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Iterators</span>.<span class=\"name\">instProductiveOfFinte</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span cl